From 89ac53e96217bd5525ee56eaa1b8ef2b398a9ad6 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Nithyanantham Paramasivam <quic_nithp@quicinc.com>
Date: Wed, 2 Apr 2025 20:55:29 +0530
Subject: [PATCH] wifi: ath12k: Enable REO queue lookup table feature on QCN9274
Git-commit: 89ac53e96217bd5525ee56eaa1b8ef2b398a9ad6
Patch-mainline: v6.16-rc1
References: jsc#PED-14425

Enable the REO queue lookup table feature for QCN9274 by setting the
reoq_lut_support flag.

Tested-on: QCN9274 hw2.0 PCI WLAN.WBE.1.3.1-00173-QCAHKSWPL_SILICONZ-1

Signed-off-by: Nithyanantham Paramasivam <quic_nithp@quicinc.com>
Reviewed-by: Vasanthakumar Thiagarajan <vasanthakumar.thiagarajan@oss.qualcomm.com>
Link: https://patch.msgid.link/20250402152529.1649402-4-quic_nithp@quicinc.com
Signed-off-by: Jeff Johnson <jeff.johnson@oss.qualcomm.com>
Acked-by: Takashi Iwai <tiwai@suse.de>

---
 drivers/net/wireless/ath/ath12k/hw.c | 2 +-
 1 file changed, 1 insertion(+), 1 deletion(-)

diff --git a/drivers/net/wireless/ath/ath12k/hw.c b/drivers/net/wireless/ath/ath12k/hw.c
index c349911c47db..e3249719ca53 100644
--- a/drivers/net/wireless/ath/ath12k/hw.c
+++ b/drivers/net/wireless/ath/ath12k/hw.c
@@ -1288,7 +1288,7 @@ static const struct ath12k_hw_params ath12k_hw_params[] = {
 		.download_calib = true,
 		.supports_suspend = false,
 		.tcl_ring_retry = true,
-		.reoq_lut_support = false,
+		.reoq_lut_support = true,
 		.supports_shadow_regs = false,
 
 		.num_tcl_banks = 48,
-- 
2.53.0

